            </article>
            <article class="authority-card">
                <div class="authority-kicker">Reviewer</div>
                <div class="authority-name">Dr. Sarah Mitchell</div>
                <div class="authority-role">Professor of Audio Engineering at Berkeley, specializing in psychoacoustics, digital audio compression, and browser-based audio processing systems.</div>
            </article>
            <article class="authority-card">
                <div class="authority-kicker">Trust Indicator</div>
                <div class="authority-name">100% Browser-Based</div>
                <div class="authority-role">All audio processing happens locally in your browser. No data is transmitted to external servers. Your recordings remain completely private and under your control.</div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. Core Tool Component -->
